"title": "6690: mercy, response to God's",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6690",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God's merciful dealings with believers should move them to show similar acts of mercy to others, as well as to rejoice in his graciousness and proclaim it to others.</p>\n<h2>The proper response to God's mercy</h2>\n<h3>A self-giving faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:1\">ROM 12:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps13:5\">PSA 13:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps52:8\">PSA 52:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:8\">EPH 2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:16\">1TI 1:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:16\">HEB 4:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:5\">1PE 5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:6\">JAS 4:6</a></p>\n<h3>A merciful attitude towards others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:36\">LUK 6:36</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:8\">MIC 6:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech7:9\">ZEC 7:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:7\">MAT 5:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:13\">MAT 9:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:27-Luke10:37\">LUK 10:27–10:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:12-Jas2:13\">JAS 2:12–2:13</a></p>\n<h3>A forgiving attitude towards others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:12\">MAT 6:12</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:4\">LUK 11:4</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:14\">MAT 6:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:21-Matt18:35\">MAT 18:21–18:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:37\">LUK 6:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:3-Luke17:4\">LUK 17:3–17:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor2:7\">2CO 2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:32\">EPH 4:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:13\">COL 3:13</a></p>\n<h3>Mercy is to be a characteristic of daily living</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:1\">HEB 13:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:37-Matt25:40\">MAT 25:37–25:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:9-Rom12:21\">ROM 12:9–12:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:23\">JUD 1:23</a></p>\n<h2>By God's mercy, the believer can persevere</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:1\">2CO 4:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:3-2Thess3:5\">2TH 3:3–3:5</a></p>\n<h2>Sharing God's grace and mercy with others</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:1\">2CO 8:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:14-2Cor5:20\">2CO 5:14–5:20</a></p>",
